chart.name: Top Operations/sec
chart.programText: A = data('counter.commands_processed', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).mean(by=['plugin_instance']).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Memory Bytes Used
chart.programText:
A = data('bytes.used_memory', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Operations/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.commands_processed', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Redis CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.used_cpu_sys', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).scale(100).publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.used_cpu_user', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).scale(100).publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.used_cpu_sys', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).scale(100).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('counter.used_cpu_user', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).scale(100).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+A).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).min().publish(label='D')
E = (C).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='E')
F = (C).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='F')
G = (C).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='G')
H = (C).max().publish(label='H')

chart.name: # Connections
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.connected_clients', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Slave Replication Offsets
chart.programText: A = data('gauge.slave_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Network Bytes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.total_net_output_bytes', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.total_net_input_bytes', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Mode
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.slave_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).count().publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.master_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).count().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B-A).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Evicted & Expired Keys /sec
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.evicted_keys', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.expired_keys', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Blocked & Rejected Clients
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.blocked_clients', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.rejected_connections', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Master Replication Offsets
chart.programText: A = data('gauge.master_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).above(1, inclusive=True).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Operations/sec
chart.programText: A = data('counter.commands_processed', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: # Connected Clients
chart.programText: A = data('gauge.connected_clients', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Lowest Cache Hit Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.keyspace_hits', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).mean(by=['plugin_instance']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('derive.keyspace_misses', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).mean(by=['plugin_instance']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = ((A+1)/(A+1+B)*100).bottom(count=5).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Blocked and Rejected Clients
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.blocked_clients', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.rejected_connections', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Used Memory
chart.programText: A = data('bytes.used_memory_rss', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Cache Hit Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.keyspace_hits', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('derive.keyspace_misses', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = ((A+1)/(A+1+B)*100).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).min().publish(label='D')
E = (C).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='E')
F = (C).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='F')
G = (C).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='G')
H = (C).max().publish(label='H')

chart.name: # Instances
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.slave_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).count().publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.master_repl_offset', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).count().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B-A).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Total Network Bytes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.total_net_output_bytes', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('counter.total_net_input_bytes', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info')).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Cache Hit Rate %
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.keyspace_hits', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379'), extrapolation='last_value').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('derive.keyspace_misses', filter=filter('plugin', 'redis_info') and filter('plugin_instance', 'redis-2.8.19-1:6379'), extrapolation='last_value').sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = ((A+1)/(A+1+B)*100).publish(label='C')
